               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BALLANTINE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Am I to understand you to say you believe those to be in the prisoner's writing? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes; the name "Josiah Westley," and, I should say, the column with the name of the bills—I will undertake to pledge my belief on the subject.</p>
