                        <interp inst="t18511027-name-294" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE BELLAMY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am inspector of the police at York; I have lived there fifty years, and have been in the police there twenty-five years. I have made inquiries in reference to James Gilbert, a bookseller, at York, but have heard of no such person—in the course of my inquiries I came upon a person named James Gilbert, of Sheffield, a bookseller, who sometimes goes to York.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18511027-name-295" type="witnessName">
