                  </hi>. I am a clerk, at Messr's. Glyn's. On 29th Aug. I presented this bill for 113<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. at 200, High Holborn—I found no person there who knew anything about it—I inquired at the house of the acceptor, but heard nothing of him—I left a notice at the house.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18511027-name-299" type="witnessName">
